import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; const CandidateDashboard: React.FC = () => { return (

Welcome to TalentFlow

Your gateway to exciting career opportunities. Browse jobs, apply with ease, and track your applications.

{/* Browse Jobs Card */}

Browse Jobs

Explore available positions and find your perfect match.

View Jobs
{/* Quick Apply Card */}

Quick Apply

Submit applications easily with our streamlined process.

Start Applying
{/* Assessments Card */}

Assessments

Complete job-specific assessments to showcase your skills.

Take Assessment
{/* Recent Activity Section */}

Getting Started

Application Process

  1. Browse available job positions
  2. Click "Apply Now" on jobs that interest you
  3. Fill out the application form
  4. Upload your resume (optional but recommended)
  5. Submit and wait for HR review

What to Expect

  • Response within 5-7 business days
  • Possible skills assessment for some positions
  • Interview invitations for selected candidates
  • Regular updates on your application status
); }; export default CandidateDashboard;
